metadata.title: Piper J-3 Cub
aws::graph::propositions: J-3 is a civil variant of the Piper J-3 Cub.
J-3 is equipped with a Continental A-40 engine of 37 hp (28 kW).
J-3 is equipped with a Continental A-40-2 engine of 37 hp (28 kW).
J-3 is equipped with a Continental A-40-3 engine of 37 hp (28 kW).
J-3 is equipped with a Continental A-40-4 engine of 40 hp (30 kW).

J3C-40 is equipped with a Continental A-40-5 engine of 40 hp (30 kW).
J3C-50 is a civil variant of the Piper J-3 Cub.
J3C-50 is equipped with a Continental A-50-1 engine of 50 hp (37 kW).
J3C-50 is equipped with Continental A-50-2 to A-50-9 engines of 50 hp (37 kW).
J3C-50S is a civil variant of the Piper J-3 Cub.
J3C-50S is equipped with a Continental A-50-1 engine of 50 hp (37 kW).
J3C-50S is equipped with Continental A-50-2 to A-50-9 engines of 50 hp (37 kW).

### Civil
J-3
Equipped with a Continental A-40, A-40-2, or A-40-3 engine of 37 hp (28 kW), or A-40-4 engine of 40 hp (30 kW)
J3C-40
Certified 14 July 1938 and equipped with a Continental A-40-4 or A-40-5 of 40 hp (30 kW)
J3C-50
